ing\n- **Start date:** Begin early - regression concepts take time\n\n### 🟡 **UPCOMING DEADLINES**\n\n**Quiz 2: Sampling Distributions - March 6 (20 points)**\n- **Timing:** Just before midterm\n- **Content:** Week 7-8 material (Sampling distributions, CLT)\n\n**Final Project: Statistical Report - May 8 (100 points)**\n- **Weight:** 25% of final grade\n- **Start planning:** After midterm completion\n\n### 🎯 **Strategic Recommendations**\n\n**Based on your B+ performance trend:**\n1. **Target the midterm** - A strong midterm (85%+) could push you to B+ overall\n2. **Leverage homework strength** - Your consistent B+ on HW1/HW2 shows solid understanding\n3. **Focus on regression early** - Start HW3 concepts now while studying for midterm\n\n**Study plan for next 3 weeks:**\n- **Week 1:** Midterm review + Sampling distributions quiz\n- **Week 2:** Midterm exam + Begin regression concepts\n- **Week 3:** Deep dive into regression + Start HW3\n\n**Would you like me to create a detailed study schedule for the midterm, or would you prefer to focus on getting ahead with HW3 first?**","state":"done"}]},"chatId":"general-chat","recordedAt":"2026-02-28T20:03:03.734Z"}
